00:57:18,200 --> 00:57:19,999
Penculikan, pemerasan, fitnah!

962
00:57:19,999 --> 00:57:21,670
Baik. Baiklah.

963
00:57:21,670 --> 00:57:24,569
Pak Lee. Langsung pergi ke kantor polisi.

